criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  absence of acute or chronic pain disorders;

          -  no reports of psychiatric, cognitive and /or neurological disorders;

          -  no drugs including, analgesics or anti-anxiety medications on regular use (except for
             oral contraceptives).

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  pregnant or breast-feeding;

          -  unable to give informed consent, communicate and understand the purpose and the
             instructions of the study.
